Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.17,Dia-JPN,,0,0,0,,すみません、人違いです
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.17,0:03:53.63,Dia-CN,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:53.63,Dia-JPN,,0,0,0,,いいえ
